soot.toDex.instructions

Class Insn22b

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.toDex.instructions.AbstractInsn
      • soot.toDex.instructions.Insn22b
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Insn, OneRegInsn, TwoRegInsn

    public class Insn22b
extends AbstractInsn
implements TwoRegInsn
    The "22b" instruction format: It needs two 16-bit code units, has two registers and is used for a 8-bit literal (hence the "b" for "byte").

    It is used by the "/lit8" opcodes for binary operations.
